animeTitle: Doraemon Movie 39: Nobita no Getsumen Tansaki
otherNames: Doraemon the Movie 2019: Chronicle of the Moon Exploration, 映画 ドラえもん のび太の月面探査記
synopsis: Nobita no Getsumen Tansaki is an original story centered around the Isetsu Club Member Badge gadget featured in volume 23 of the original Doraemon manga. It is the first Doraemon film to feature a solo female screenwriter.
